1. Transcode validation (#6) - Critical for data safety
2. Valid/Invalid modes (#3) - Important for handling broken files
3. Archive handling (#1) - Significant space savings
4. Text processing (#2) - Additional format support
5. Advanced video/audio (#4, #5) - Edge cases
